{"type":"message","id":"16561f37","parentId":"e5fb3bb6","timestamp":"2026-06-11T01:12:23.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to install a skill. They shared a folder key `file_v3_0112i_6850ac55-fc5b-4c99-ab26-1486d1d9507g` with name `miaoshou-erp-source-import`. This looks like a ClawHub skill package reference. Let me read the find-skills skill to understand how to install skills from ClawHub.\n","thinkingSignature":"bda141f20ef6e57d93806e1935f259d9491bb3c4d7523c04e2702f9290b35f04"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0e397d700e23451693fc028d","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":56340,"output":128,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56468,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781140338241,"responseId":"06793e739c124638e6afa765f9453f01"}}
{"type":"message","id":"df06c303","parentId":"16561f37","timestamp":"2026-06-11T01:12:23.704Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_0e397d700e23451693fc028d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: \"Search, install, update, sync, or publish agent skills with the ClawHub CLI and registry.\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781140343704}}
