{"type":"message","id":"ef28eaa3","parentId":"d30af680","timestamp":"2026-06-11T01:25:39.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The skill is now properly installed. Let me verify the full listing.\n","thinkingSignature":"51b02281962f122a1173542f75f8320d6c0af8e751e0705d72ffc14d326cebf7"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n✅ **Skill 已安装完成**\n\n```\nskills/miaoshou-erp-source-import/\n├── SKILL.md              # 技能说明\n├── assets/\n│   ├── icon.png\n│   └── icon.svg\n├── references/\n│   └── api-spec.md       # API规格\n└── resources/\n    └── config.json.example  # 配置示例\n```\n\n**使用前需要配置：**\n1. 复制 `resources/config.json.example` → `resources/config.json`\n2. 填入 `app_key` 和 `app_secret`（来自妙手ERP开放平台）\n3. 可选：设置环境变量 `MIAOSHOU_APP_KEY` 和 `MIAOSHOU_APP_SECRET`\n\n需要我帮你配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":189,"output":167,"cacheRead":67392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67748,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781141131948,"responseId":"0679418ccf3c1819991a9da009c1fbf0"}}
