{"type":"message","id":"986938db","parentId":"3a96ba0e","timestamp":"2026-06-11T01:32:51.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user confirmed they saw the successful collection. They were asking about making the environment variables persistent. Let me update the SKILL.md to read from the config.json file as a fallback, since we couldn't set environment variables persistently. Or I can create a wrapper script that the skill uses.\n\nActually, let me think about the cleanest approach. The SKILL.md already mentions two ways to configure:\n1. `resources/config.json`\n2. Environment variables\n\nSince we couldn't set environment variables persistently, I should make sure the skill can read from `config.json`. Let me check if the current test was using environment variables (which worked) or if I should update the skill to use config.json.\n\n\nThe test worked because the exec command set environment variables inline, but that won't work across restarts. I need to update the SKILL.md to use config.json as the primary configuration method, then verify the miaoshou skill is actually reading from it correctly. Since the test succeeded with inline env vars, I know the API works—the issue is just persistence for future sessions.\n","thinkingSignature":"fb7f6f1060324e6c884cccd26cf357134893a65c0c2ee005442f25a8a095a1b1"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白，测试成功了。环境变量的问题是 exec 里设置的在重启后不保留。\n\n**最可靠的持久化方案** — 既然 SKILL.md 已支持从 `resources/config.json` 读取，我之前已经创建了 config.json。\n\n问题是 skill 里的签名逻辑目前可能没读取 config.json。让我更新一下，确保其他 skill 和重启后都能用：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b2b8ad44c6bc478f9a28fe98","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# 妙手ERP签名工具\n# 用法: ./miaoshou-sign.sh <path> <body_json>\n# 或直接 source 导入函数: source miaoshou-sign.sh\n\nCONFIG_FILE=\"$(dirname \"$0\")/resources/config.json\"\n\nget_config() {\n  local key=\"$1\"\n  grep -o \"\\\"${key}\\\"[[:space:]]*:[[:space:]]*\\\"[^\\\"]*\\\"\" \"$CONFIG_FILE\" | head -1 | sed 's/.*:[[:space:]]*\"//' | sed 's/\"$//'\n}\n\nAPP_KEY=\"${MIAOSHOU_APP_KEY:*** 'app_key')}\"\nAPP_SECRET=\"${MIA…:*** 'app_secret')}\"\nBASE_URL=\"${MIAOSHOU_BASE_URL:-$(grep 'base_url' \"$CONFIG_FILE\" | cut -d'\"' -f4)}\"\n\nif [ -z \"$APP_KEY\" ] || [ -z \"$APP_SECRET\" ]; then\n  echo \"Error: MIAOSHOU_APP_KEY and MIAOSHOU_APP_SECRET must be set or in config.json\" >&2\n  exit 1\nfi\n\nsign_request() {\n  local path=\"$1\"\n  local body=\"$2\"\n  local timestamp\n  timestamp=$(date +%s)\n  \n  local data=\"${APP_SECRET}${path}${timestamp}${APP_KEY}${body}${APP_SECRET}\"\n  local sign\n  sign=$(echo -n \"$data\" | openssl dgst -sha256 -hmac \"$APP_SECRET\" | awk '{print $2}')\n  \n  echo \"$timestamp:$sign\"\n}\n\nif [ \"$#\" -ge 2 ]; then\n  result=$(sign_request \"$1\" \"$2\")\n  timestamp=$(echo \"$result\" | cut -d: -f1)\n  sign=$(echo \"$result\" | cut -d: -f2)\n  echo \"x-app-key: $APP_KEY\"\n  echo \"x-timestamp: $timestamp\"\n  echo \"x-sign: $sign\"\nfi","path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/skills/miaoshou-erp-source-import/sign.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6950,"output":772,"cacheRead":81955,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89677,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781141544025,"responseId":"067943281c99001656c93a7a638e8b41"}}
