{"type":"message","id":"d4d1c32d","parentId":"c8e5107e","timestamp":"2026-06-11T01:33:50.490Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sign.sh script is now working correctly and reading from config.json. The config.json has the full credentials.\n\nNow for persistence across restarts - the skill should work because it reads from config.json. The environment variables in ~/.bashrc are a fallback but aren't needed since config.json is the primary configuration method.\n\nLet me tell the user the setup is complete and persistent.\n","thinkingSignature":"6f6ad3f723200c9671e593ffdaae41893da4ec3f5217c003f0da3964c5bb9347"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**✅ 持久化完成**\n\nconfig.json 已写入完整凭证（重启后仍有效）：\n```\nresources/config.json\n├── app_key: ak_03d60381f9ed401b9e825942864a477b\n├── app_secret: 6b7b34…2e87 (完整)\n├── base_url: https://openapi-erp.91miaoshou.com\n└── timeout: 30\n```\n\n`sign.sh` 脚本也已就绪，其他 skill 调用时会从 config.json 读取凭证。重启后不需要重新配置。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4859,"output":193,"cacheRead":86321,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91373,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781141621260,"responseId":"06794375cd3b7c356fff376309e77947"}}
